Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.62,2:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,竹子
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.46,2:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.80,2:02:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.97,2:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:02:37.47,2:02:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:02:54.49,2:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,2:03:12.13,2:03:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,8月15日
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.88,2:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这一天终于还是来临了
